0195|*Keyboard sucros
0197|*The functions of selected keys can be redefined by the sucro technique.
0198|*It is possible to alter the tasks of all regular typewriter keys.
0200|*When a keyboard sucro is activated, it normally gives a message (on the
0201|*bottom line) about the changes of the keyboard functions.
0202|*The keyboard sucro is terminated usually by the '#' key and then normal
0203|*keyboard functions are resumed.
0205|*Standard keyboard sucros have been created, for example, for typing
0206|*shadow characters (/S), for typing box graphics characters (/BOX), and
0207|*for writing sucro code (/SUCRO).
0208|*A list of keyboard sucros and other sucro tools is obtained by activating
0209|*the sucro
0210|*/SUCROS
